{"tid":797774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係港大😤] 港大精算尖子夏健祺宿舍三次偷拍女生裸體 被判感化18月🙌","createTime":"2018-08-28T18:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T17:39:52.000Z","uid":161050,"like":7,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0d324251cc58ce711ecdb1c299ca79a775952e08","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"<em><ins>#HaCodyJims</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/104650_9633bdc271363bb6674c85b86214771a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F104650_9633bdc271363bb6674c85b86214771a.jpeg&h=234412c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獲獎學金升讀<span style=\"color: red;\">港大精算</span>系的男學生，去年<span style=\"color: red;\">三度在港大宿舍一名女宿生的房間內裝置攝錄機，偷拍她裸體</span>的片段，影片卻同時拍到男生在調整鏡頭，女生發現攝錄機後報警。精算系男生早前承認三項不誠實使用電腦罪，今(16日)在東區法院<span style=\"color: red;\">判18個月感化</span>。裁判官相信<span style=\"color: red;\">本案只是單一事件，被告已汲取教訓。</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>整個家庭深受打擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n被告<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>夏健祺，21歲</strong></span>，承認去年4月至7月期間，三度在港大聖約翰學院宿舍內偷拍住在同一宿舍，但並不相熟的同齡女事主。<br />\n<br />\n被告早前求情時透露，他從<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國回流返港，在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳統名校培正中學畢業</span>後，獲奬學金升讀港大精算系。夏的父親是公務員，母親則為行政人員，</span></strong>兩年內會退休，所以對夏寄予厚望，他犯下偷拍案令整個家庭深受打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>求情稱應付考試及運動比賽壓力大</strong><br />\n<br />\n辯方律師曾稱被告面對<span style=\"color: red;\">校內考試和應付運動比賽，感到很大壓力，更出現抑鬱徵狀，最終因衝動犯案</span>，事後已感到非常後悔。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官錢禮判刑時，接納報告指被告適合判感化多於社會服務令，相信他是一個得到家庭支持的年輕人，本案屬單一事件，被告已從中汲取教訓，<span style=\"color: red;\">重犯機會低</span>。報告原本建議判12個月感化，但裁判官認為判處18個月感化更適合，被告需要遵從感化官的指示學習和工作、接受心理精神輔導，及參與有益更生的社區活動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>女事主發現書架上有微型攝錄機揭發</strong><br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年7月女事主發現宿舍書架上有一部微型攝錄機，她打開查看，發現內藏記憶卡，內有她裸體的片段，亦見到被告事前調整鏡頭。女事主立即告知男友，被告知道事情敗露，曾向女事主承認偷拍，但其男友最後仍將此事告知宿舍職員報警。警方調查後，在被告電腦搜出13段偷拍影片，當中有事主裸體的影片，被告被捕後亦承認，他早於4月第一次放攝錄機在女事主房間，5月再放一次，事件曝光已經是他<span style=\"color: red;\">第三次</span>用攝錄機偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1110/2017<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/105315/港大精算高才生認宿舍偷拍女生裸體片-被判感化18月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F105315%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B2%BE%E7%AE%97%E9%AB%98%E6%89%8D%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%A3%B8%E9%AB%94%E7%89%87-%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%9618%E6%9C%88&d=Vr7JYjVqTURLvFwOphuC9wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3f61c569\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/105315/港大精算高才生認宿舍偷拍女生裸體片-被判感化18月</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/431113-香港-港大精算尖子認偷拍宿舍女同學+求情將考專業試\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F431113-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B2%BE%E7%AE%97%E5%B0%96%E5%AD%90%E8%AA%8D%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%2B%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E5%B0%87%E8%80%83%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E8%A9%A6&d=Vr7JYjVqTURLvFwOphuC9wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e9ba0083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F431113-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%B2%BE%E7%AE%97%E5%B0%96%E5%AD%90%E8%AA%8D%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%2B%E6%B1%82%E6%83%85%E5%B0%87%E8%80%83%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E8%A9%A6&h=e32807f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/431113-香港-港大精算尖子認偷拍宿舍女同學+求情將考專業試</a></span>"},{"pid":"16b479ea216e90d17c5a3e2136b3fb8420055d9b","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:37:43.000Z","msg":"🎥💾💻🍆💦🤤😜"},{"pid":"d032284c3f2dd8b23facd1e2b16f4ee88a799764","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":2,"dislike":45,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:41:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">祺　感化還好嗎　尚愛拍少女裸體嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近　近乎沒露面　你有新對象嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n＊真想你帶我見　你剛識到的她<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　我想聽你意見　這算是病吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　為何無論你　願意怎樣試<br />\n　怎樣也不可抗拒去偷拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>(怎樣也沒令自己戀上她)<br />\n<br />\n＃<span style=\"color: red;\">難道沒打J太耐　精子都谷上腦袋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　試圖再努力愛　也顯得不自在<br />\n　不懂得如何談戀愛　還是我太愛你　對過去太放不開<br />\n<br />\n△難道是寂寞太耐　生鏽的鎖不能開<br />\n　鑰匙也拆斷了　留在舊患所在<br />\n　懷內　放滿對你的愛　難怪跟誰也　再沒法戀愛<br />\n<br />\n我　有時仍很怕　路過你那從前的家<br />\n往事若然未落幕　再揭起有害嗎<br />\n<br />\nRepeat (＊),＃,△<br />\n<br />\n難道沒練習太耐　感覺都追不回來<br />\n試圖再努力愛　也顯得不自在<br />\n耿耿於懷從前的愛　從沒有振作過　痛了再痛也應該<br />\n<br />\n難道是寂寞太耐　生鏽的鎖不能開<br />\n往事卻似斷箭　還剩下在體內<br />\n若懷內　放滿對你的愛　害怕一直也　再沒法戀愛"},{"pid":"99a4967adff20b7c52fa0f226bf86c043059df9d","tid":797774,"uid":151904,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"偷拍人渣仆街死<br />\n屌你老母自己上網睇鹹片打飛機啦<br />\n要屌閪咪去叫雞囉<br />\non撚9"},{"pid":"afb128cc34bab62d8234bf661f7942157da4bc15","tid":797774,"uid":41130,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:50:03.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},{"pid":"cecf1970417a5124ad0c156b45a3cab57760b4fd","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"99a4967adff20b7c52fa0f226bf86c043059df9d","tid":797774,"uid":151904,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:46:52.000Z","msg":"偷拍人渣仆街死<br />\n屌你老母自己上網睇鹹片打飛機啦<br />\n要屌閪咪去叫雞囉<br />\non撚9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:53:36.000Z","msg":"難道沒打J太耐　精子都谷上腦袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d790044576d6ed4e139a97356e5f2661e7c6d392","tid":797774,"uid":77314,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"繼續鞭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港大學加1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3548149cd453e28d58b447922eaa8e751e7c91","tid":797774,"uid":2748,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"樓主，你同佢好大仇口？出咗4次post嗱喎"},{"pid":"a9321961ac48ac9d1e7410c43d0c4fa0f0a710a6","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afb128cc34bab62d8234bf661f7942157da4bc15","tid":797774,"uid":41130,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T18:50:03.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/16/153046/GCvf4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F153046%2FGCvf4.png&h=b9508cea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31cefb21af990c90da5249927f5ed3acc7bf312","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5b3548149cd453e28d58b447922eaa8e751e7c91","tid":797774,"uid":2748,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T19:00:27.000Z","msg":"樓主，你同佢好大仇口？出咗4次post嗱喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T20:00:06.000Z","msg":"都係提醒下Ha Cody Jims 啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4bcdd39de05d0c146854ba7a4925c1e692d4a1","tid":797774,"uid":161050,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T20:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/040141_b2268fed3e7697b08fdd34108543aaa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2